{"tid":1611740,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【贊唔贊成】今個星期六/日：賀佢老母 第二回？","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:19:28.000Z","uid":161430,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc887afc55977566f1c8ab4ed829d5eab1bcd76","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"老母賀一次唔夠，緊係要吸收上次經驗，<br />\n黎個再進步少少既，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>賀佢老母 Round 2：<br />\n對準政權，同時繼續清算殺中學生既黑警</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n時間：十月五或六 (星期六/日)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*提提你 下星期一係紅假，今個禮拜有連假係大好時機</span><br />\n<br />\n地區：六區開花<br />\n<br />\n出到去：有Object咁去行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n贊成，刻不容緩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了，等呢個禮拜過左先算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15781f55d0a3ebdbc1210eab353dd81e587d274","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59743fd84c0198a50295e2e7360de19431d2b2a","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dbbfc99272f3cd66903ec8bb5ab47087673c4c","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee0c126ab308028f69070b9b1dda890814e5d23","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5245401a8814d4ba253ed78b7d59e80eb111b52","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cc6acad21a72c72d6f88e2cbc9b26ad4964732","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13e64e81cf262a99b456ac8de19a03067a46001","tid":1611740,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"又六區開花?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e77e0f0793fae2f01de65f83c5a72bb463d6ce","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7346dcd8697dd9984e3e85cb0303e55bdac1519","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c13e64e81cf262a99b456ac8de19a03067a46001","tid":1611740,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"又六區開花?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"地區再集體定<br />\n但首先睇下個日子，係咪決定今個禮拜食住上先<br />\n呢樣要表左態先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729a8374455b9a98516a7db6d018cf9ff033d5c3","tid":1611740,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49dd08dad7d3bed45f067d9899b4c7f409b4e142","tid":1611740,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"讚成要有行動，詳細要再傾"},{"pid":"b95923c181b63bbb93928918fdc25b2546353008","tid":1611740,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實十一之所以聚到人喺港島北又其他7、8區同時多人係因為有足夠宣傳同有時間俾人預出席<br />\n距離星期六、日得返3、4日，我怕唔夠時間宣傳<br />\n好似罷工咁，85多人過92罷係因為宣傳咗成個月，十一都有2、3星期"},{"pid":"27f73ca9c08cf22a74a22ddea79098123d1ddc69","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">下個禮拜一就有紅假</span><br />\n<br />\n即係熱愛返工 唔想罷工既香港人<br />\n今個禮拜六日有充足時間心你出去賀老母<br />\n而星期一仲可以「罷工」唔駛返工<br />\n<br />\n而家今日都係二號<br />\n唔係叫你即日 聽日就行動<br />\n文宣有時間做 做完岩岩好時晨到<br />\n<br />\n等幾日亦唔會又等多個禮拜搞到又冷卻左<br />\n<br />\n我自己就睇唔到有咩藉口<br />\n喺個中學生比心射心口之後，<br />\n之後個禮拜六或者日咁樣都唔出黎，<br />\n仲要等"},{"pid":"438d0cb2798f77d1891575669ca363ab7a4b4813","tid":1611740,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95923c181b63bbb93928918fdc25b2546353008","tid":1611740,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實十一之所以聚到人喺港島北又其他7、8區同時多人係因為有足夠宣傳同有時間俾人預出席<br />\n距離星期六、日得返3、4日，我怕唔夠時間宣傳<br />\n好似罷工咁，85多人過92罷係因為宣傳咗成個月，十一都有2、3星期"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"突然喺3、4日後大搞，怕唔怕唔夠人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ea1a420538ab29e53b50b4adbedc0db41f9a3c","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95923c181b63bbb93928918fdc25b2546353008","tid":1611740,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實十一之所以聚到人喺港島北又其他7、8區同時多人係因為有足夠宣傳同有時間俾人預出席<br />\n距離星期六、日得返3、4日，我怕唔夠時間宣傳<br />\n好似罷工咁，85多人過92罷係因為宣傳咗成個月，十一都有2、3星期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"罷工難宣傳，因為本身就極多人罷啦起，返少日工都唔得，但遊行示威呢類，我覺得即日或者一日時間係難宣傳<br />\n<br />\n不過等幾日而且又有開真槍事件，我個人覺得夠時間"},{"pid":"ea53246b0522f9d7620879d12ee22516207c800a","tid":1611740,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438d0cb2798f77d1891575669ca363ab7a4b4813","tid":1611740,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95923c181b63bbb93928918fdc25b2546353008","tid":1611740,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit